⁣
I thought I would share some questions that have been helpful for me within my practice: ⁣
⁣
🌱 What do I need in this moment? ⁣
 🌱 How can I be in contact to my higher self? ⁣
🌱 What thoughts am I attaching myself to?⁣
🌱 What things can I let go of for this time? ⁣
🌱 Do I need to attach to opinions and thoughts? ⁣
⁣
For me beginning to find an answer to any of these questions comes from...⁣
⁣
Being aware of how I am breathing all the time. When my breath is fluid, then I physically flow through my life. I try to just let what I think about something go, and just observed it all. ⁣
I use my breath to surrender to what I’m seeing. ⁣
⁣
And I carefully remind myself...⁣
I am here only to be truly helpful. ⁣
I am here to represent he who sent me. ⁣
I do not have to worry about what to do or say because he who sent me will direct me. ⁣
I am content to be where he sends me knowing he is with me also. ⁣
I am being healed as he teaches me to heal. ⁣
⁣
💚💚💚⁣
